code: @Override protected synchronized AsyncProcessor chooseProcessor(AsyncProcessor[] processors, Exchange exchange) {     int randomWeight = ThreadLocalRandom.current().nextInt(runtimeRatioSum).     int choiceWeight = 0.     int index = 0.     while (true) {         DistributionRatio ratio = getRatios().get(index).         choiceWeight += ratio.getRuntimeWeight().         if (randomWeight < choiceWeight) {             ratio.decrement().             decrementSum().             lastIndex = index.             return processors[index].         }         index++.     } }
